news.title: Strata receives license for SM REIT from Sebi
news.para: Strata aims to initially launch up to six SM REIT schemes in FY26, and gradually increase it to one scheme every month.

news.title: Singapore's Aelios raises offer to buy rest of Suntec REIT at $2.5 billion valuation
news.para: Aelios, owned by billionaire couple Gordon and Celine Tang, raised the offer to S$1.19 per share, up from the previous bid made in December of S$1.16 apiece.

news.title: Punjab government acquires 167 flats for IAS,IPS officers in Purab apartments
news.para: The Punjab govt already deposited Rs 38,85,42,000, including 2% cancer cess and 2% Purab Premium Apartment Corpus Fund, with GMADA against the total payment of Rs 1,00,48,50,000.
